{"tid":2428338,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文在寅稱政府已做好準備隨時與日方面對面會談","createTime":"2021-03-01T12:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T13:55:17.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdda1991379892885ea8f18363f00dc412348de7","tid":2428338,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"南韓總統文在寅說政府做好準備，隨時與日本政府面對面會談。<br />\n<br />\n文在寅在一項紀念活動上說，兩國有不幸歷史，就算加害者可以忘記歷史，但受害者決不會忘記。他說事過多年，雙方已互為重要鄰國，應以史為鑒，但不能被歷史拖後腿。文在寅又指南韓政府將站在受害者立場，尋求明智的解決方案，但同時不會停止為韓日兩國合作及未來發展，付出努力。<br />\n<br />\n南韓與日本因慰安婦及二戰勞工索賠問題，關係降至冰點，評論認為文在寅的發言，是向日方拋出願意對話的信息，日方將如何反應，值得關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578143-20210301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578143-20210301.htm&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt10wAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=47f41baf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578143-20210301.htm&h=db190d73\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578143-20210301.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7ea53b9862ed7e4f8beed425088c17896aa87886","tid":2428338,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"日韓台結盟，食盡亞洲生意"},{"pid":"f49c13700e99ac9ef3f33824e997ccd0781963b7","tid":2428338,"uid":352873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"韓狗又定時定後出黎R慰安婦賠償 屌佢老母"},{"pid":"ddc4a6d6f4b3f6901b73b7970fbde1ab13b6d1c0","tid":2428338,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"共同舐共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156598eda54a063005d692df3610f010acf6477a","tid":2428338,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:53:30.000Z","msg":"你成日提慰安婦好難同你開心交流合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfacb47020a163